      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; boundary condition equivalency is documented qualitatively.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency assessment of input parameters between validation and COU scenarios is not required at MRL 2. The validation experiments use the same nominal geometry and operating conditions as the COU. Any dimensional deviations between the physical test article and the CAD model are documented and assessed as negligible for the hemolysis QoI."
    }
